Text:
A new cooking competition series that takes its contestants around the world to test their skills in some of the world’s greatest – and most demanding – restaurants.

Season 01, Episode 01 – “London Calling”
Twelve chefs compete in a globe-spanning culinary race in this reality series. The premiere episode’s destination is London, where the players learn about regional food culture and participate in a pub crawl. Appearing: Nigella Lawson.
